content.text: Preserves indefinite states while inverting definite ones: | Input | Output | Rationale | |-------|--------|-----------| | O | Z | Standard negation | | Z | O | Standard negation | | Ø | Ø | Negation of singularity remains singular | | ∞ | ∞ | Negation of chaos is still chaos | | Ψ | Ψ | Negation of metaphor is another metaphor |
